            </div>
        
                
                            <div id="s-lg-book-desc-62383557" class="s-lg-book-desc">
                Important resource for bibliographic information concerning the many publications of the words and music of the Star-Spangled Banner. Includes a directory of early American music publishers as well as information about lithographers and artists working in the music publishing industry.
